==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Redeliver
<hw>Re`de*liv"er</hw> <pr>(r?`d?*l?v"?r)</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<sn>1.</sn> <def>To deliver or give back; to return.</def>
<rj><au>Ay<?/iffe.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>To deliver or liberate a second time or
again.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>To report; to deliver the answer of.</def>
<mark>[R.]</mark> ⟦ldquo⟧Shall I <xex>redeliver</xex> you e'en
so?⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Shak.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Redeliverance</ent>⟦br⟧
